‘In 2020, we kept our promises, 2021 we shall do more’ – T Pumpy sends message to subscribers, Nigerians as they celebrate Christmas The management of T Pumpy Concept Limited, developers of Abuja-based T Pumpy Estates, has sent out heartwarming messages to her esteemed subscribers and Nigerians at large as they join the rest of the world to mark this year’s Christmas. Christmas, which is the commemoration of the birth of Jesus Christ, is celebrated annually worldwide among Christians on 25 December. The company with 22 housing estate units spread across Guzape, Lugbe, Karasana, Kyami, Wawa, Jabi, Katampe, Kuje and others, said although the outgoing year came with its challenges, they have been able to keep their own promises. Mr. Akintayo Adaralegbe, in a statement personally signed and made available to newsmen on Friday, assured that in the year 2021, T Pumpy will do more. He said, “It has been a challenging year but we thank God because we have been able to keep our promises. 2021 will be a busy year as we promise to do more.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-860486" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.02.40-AM-1.jpeg" alt="" width="621" height="877" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.02.40-AM-1.jpeg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.02.40-AM-1-212x300.jpeg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> “This year, we announced slashes in prices of lands in our estate through a series of our promo just to encourage people. “The last batch of the promo is still ongoing and will end December 31. It offers prospective home owners opportunities to purchase a plot of land for the sum of N1.5m instead of the market value N2.5m at its Kuje estate, giving them a huge 40 per cent discount. “We will continue to play our part in ensuring that every Nigerian owns a house.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-860483" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM.jpeg" alt="" width="960" height="540" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM.jpeg 960w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM-300x169.jpeg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px"> “As we celebrate this year’s Christmas, which commemorates the birth of our Lord Jesus Christ, we should try to spread love and care to the needy. “May we continue to walk in love, which is the reason for the season.” Pumpy Concept LTD, a registered company that deals in the sales of lands and estate plots since 2009, has over the past ten years built a reputation as an industry-acclaimed off-site home design and construction.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-860484" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM-1.jpeg" alt="" width="1080" height="720" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM-1.jpeg 1080w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM-1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.54.15-AM-1-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"> T. Pumpy Concept Limited is a progressive property developer that prides itself on its proven track records, passion and commitment to deliver superior value in design, quality and services in our developments to our customers.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-860485" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.02.39-AM.jpeg" alt="" width="621" height="877" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/WhatsApp-Image-2020-12-25-at-7.02.39-AM.jpeg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12